.head 4 -  Description: Flemings default dialog with child table window and
relevant table actions with default colours
Has database field left top and current date time
right top
ON PAM_SETINSTANCEVARS
  always
    Set sDatabase = SqlDatabase
  as needed
    Set sHelpFileName = 'n:\apps\gutpa\help\help.txt'
    Set sAboutDlgName = 'dlgAbout' - THIS IS DEFAULT
    
bAddRowsAllowed allows table action add rows allowed
bSaveRowsAllowed allows table action save changes allowed
bClearRowsAllowed allows table action clear selections allowed
bDeleteRowsAllowed allows table action delete rows allowed
bUnDeleteRowsAllowed allows table action undelete rows allowed
bOrderTableAllowed allows table action order table allowed
bMoveUpDownRowsAllowed allows table action move selected
  rows up or down one by coping them up or down.
bQueryTableAllowed allows quering of table
bTablePrintReportAllowed allows printing of table report
bSelectPbEnable allows pbSelect
bExitOnSelect if true saldestroywindow on select else just hide window
bQueryOnSelect if true and bSelectPbEnableb then calls table query
  else populates table on creation 
